  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare plaque burden in the coronary and carotid arteries 5
      years after adjuvant radiotherapy in women with right sided breast cancer vs left sided
      breast cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study reviews case series of patients with a history of breast cancer treated with
      radiotherapy for at least five years. The study measures atherosclerosis by using coronary
      and carotid artery calcium scoring.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
